title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1988-07-16
lineage: PCM Master (Sony SLV-M20HF) > Sony PCM-601ESD > Behringer Ultramatch Pro >Tascam DA-3000 (16-bit/44.1k) > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/16
description:
Set 1

The Music Never Stopped, Sugaree, Little Red Rooster, Loser, Memphis Blues, Far From Me, Bird Song

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower, I Know You Rider, Looks Like Rain, Terrapin Station, Drums, I Will Take You Home, The Other One, Stella Blue, Around & Around, One More Saturday Night, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

* W/ Baba O;atunji. Rex Benefit, FM Broadcast KPFA Berkeley Alexander Gradsky Played between sets.
